dc_title_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines for the east, west and north shores of Newark Bay, New Jersey
dc_description_s: Map of pierhead and bulkhead lines for the east, west and north shores of Newark Bay, New Jersey, extending on the East Shore from the approved lines at Bergen Neck to the N.Y. & N.R.R. bridge across the Hackensack River; on the West Shore from the approved lines at Elizabethport to the N.Y. & N.R.R. bridge across the Passaic River; and on the North Shore from the N.Y. & N.R.R. bridge across the Hackensack River to the N.Y. & N.R.R. bridge across the Passaic River. As recommended by the New York Harbor Line Board.
